c: 9
v: 81
t: "Bajabula labo ababesalele ngemumva ngokusalela ngemumva kwabo kwesithunywa sikaMvelinqangi futhi babengakuthandi ukuzabalaza kanzima ngengcebo yabo nangemiphefumulo yabo endleleni kaMvelinqangi futhi bathi, “ningayi ekushiseni” ithi “umlilo wesihogo ushisa kakhulu ukube babekuqonda (lokho)”"